name: Bulu Box Original
long_desc: This box provides a well-rounded sampling of all things health and nutrition. Each box contains 4 to 5 premium samples such as sports nutrition, sleep, and healthy snacks. Plus lifestyle extras like gym gift cards or DVDs to cover all aspects of health! Boxes ship on the 15th of every month.
short_desc: Bulu Box is the first health, nutrition and weight loss discovery box designed to help you feel your best. Each month, you'll get a box curated with a new mix of 4-5 premium samples from top brands to try.
bullets: The first health box<<<>>>4-5 premium samples<<<>>>Featuring top brands<<<>>>Includes lifestyle extras
brief: BuluBox is a monthly box of healthy discoveries that will upgrade your health.

name: GlossyBox
long_desc: Take the hassle out of choosing between brands and new makeup products with GLOSSYBOX. With a GLOSSYBOX subscription you'll also receive samples of the best hair products and the best skin care products for women. Your GLOSSYBOX will contain only the top beauty products from well known luxury brands and up-and-coming niche brands.
short_desc: GLOSSYBOX beauty experts curate monthly boxes filled with brands you know and love and brands you are discovering for the first time.
bullets: The first health box<<<>>>4-5 premium samples<<<>>>Featuring top brands<<<>>>Includes lifestyle extras
brief: Every month, we deliver a selection of five niche and high-end beauty treats.

name: Bocandy Big Box
long_desc: Each box contains a curated selection of candies and snacks from around the world and speciality snacks from America you've never seen. One month might include German haribo gummies, Japanese Pocky, Mexican tamarind candy, British wine gums, all-in-one s'mores from Colorado, and Bulgarian Peanut Puffs. Products are new each month and always delicious.
short_desc: Bocandy is a Candy Subscription Box from Around the World for just $15/month. Each month, we send you a box full of candy with cool info about where it came from.
bullets: International candies<<<>>>6-9 awesome items!<<<>>>Discover craft candy<<<>>>Carefully curated candy
brief: A delicious discovery of both hard-to-find imported and speciality candies.

name: Bulu Box Weight Loss
long_desc: Bulu Box is the best way to discover healthy, nutrition and weight loss products. Your samples should align with your goals. That's why we place samples in your box based on your profile! Once you sign up, you'll receive 4-5 diverse samples plus lifestyle bonus items!
short_desc: Designed specifically to help with the varying factors of weight loss, this box contains 4 to 5 premium weight loss items such as energy aids, healthy snacks, sleep aids and fat-burners. Plus bonus weight loss items like fitness gear and kitchen tools.
bullets: 4 to 5 diverse premium samples<<<>>>An assortment of items<<<>>>Designed specifically for weight loss<<<>>>Bonus weight loss items
brief: This box is the best way to discover healthy, nutrition and weight loss products.

name: SurpriseMyPet
long_desc: We are a great company that is bringing toys and treats to your pet each month.  We have made amazing partnerships and strive to send the highest quality products! We work with many small businesses and help them get their names out to thousands of people.  We also donate 10% of our profits to local pet charities and shelters.  We include toys, treats, accessories, grooming supplies and even a gift for the pet lover!
short_desc: When you sign up, every month you will receive a box in the mail with carefully selected dog supplies for your dog - anything from dog toys, bones and all-natural dog treats.
bullets: We are all about pets!<<<>>>Safe & Healthy for pets<<<>>>Top-notch products<<<>>>Save time + money
brief: SurpriseMyPet is a monthly subscription that sends out goodies to your pup!

name: Tasting Box
long_desc: We carefully handpick the tastiest artisanal product using the best sustainable ingredients to give you a taste of something special. Fall in love with the best small-batch foods crafted by independant makers from across America. Each month is a fun new theme and with the Casual Foodie Box, you'll receive 3 to 4 products each month!
short_desc: We carefully handpick the tastiest artisanal product using the best sustainable ingredients to give you a taste of something special. Fall in love with the best small-batch foods crafted by independant makers from across America.
bullets: Handpicked artisanal products<<<>>>Best sustainable ingredients<<<>>>Fun new theme each month<<<>>>3-4 tastiest products
brief: The perfect way to discover new, unique, and delicious products monthly.

name: SumoJerky
long_desc: We've been working hard to perfect our members-only gourmet jerky club and are excited to invite you to try it. You'll get to try different styles and flavors of top-rated beef jerky from the US. Join me and 2,000+ other jerky lovers by signing up to get your first box of jerky delivered! There are typically about 2-3 ounces of jerky in every bag, but bag sizes vary because we use different jerky makers every month. A serving of beef jerky is one ounce and has about 100 calories.
short_desc: We handpick the best flavors from the highest-rated jerky chefs in the US and send it to you. There are two to four servings of jerky in every bag (a serving is one ounce). All the jerky is minimally processed and minimally preserved.
bullets: Gourmet jerky makers<<<>>>We do taste tests and ingredient reviews<<<>>>Receive their best beef jerky<<<>>>Array of styles and flavors
brief: Try the world's best beef jerkies. Get 2+ brands of small batch jerky, monthly.

name: Smart Art Box
long_desc: Smart Art provides artists with diverse high quality materials that inspire and nourish creativity. Each month subscribers receive a new box featuring: A different artist that highlights their time period; 8 or more FULL SIZED art supplies; A unique project; and A pamphlet detailing a new art medium. We are committed to ensuring artists understand art and it’s many mediums throughout time in order to create a better understanding of the world around us. Smart Art’s mission is to deliver products that kindle creativity, stimulate exciting new techniques and establish a deeper connection with art for all.
short_desc: Monthly art projects, shipped free to your door. Subscription based art box to help boost your creativity and inspire you to make a more beautiful world.
bullets: 8+ Full Sized art supplies<<<>>>Different art theme each time<<<>>>High quality materials<<<>>>Stimulates creativity and new techniques
brief: Every month, receive high quality materials that inspire creativity.

name: A Kitchen Box
long_desc: Our subscription box delivers the element of surprise shipped to your door every month! With product and inspiration for curious cooks of every skill level, we design each box around a theme, bringing you recipes, artisan foods, our favorite kitchen tools, music, and more. Our mission is to build kitchen confidence and encourage brilliant cooking. Have more fun in the kitchen with A Kitchen Box!
short_desc: Each month we bring you a box designed around a theme, along with recipes, artisan foods, our favorite kitchen tools, music, and more.
bullets: Fits any skill level<<<>>>Encourages brilliant cooking<<<>>>Recipes, tools, artisan foods, and more<<<>>>Bringing fun to the kitchen
brief: Each month we bring creativity and fun to your kitchen with A Kitchen Box!
